spans.text: 'twas my design , Calmly to list thy Notes Divine , That I responsive Lays might send , To gain a cold Platonic Friend
Ah ! when I deemed such joys at hand , Remorseless
Cursed Power ! that to myself unknown
more on VIRGIL's tomb I'll muse
What time the rich Nile overflows
Wander the secret groves among , Where HOMER waked the immortal Song
